                        <a href="/articles/bc-pnp-refusal-appeal-reconsideration-guide-2026" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">
                            BC PNP Refusal: Appeal & Reconsideration Guide →
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/articles/bc-pnp-processing-times" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">
